  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/a2ba75f22cdc504d55f29cfe779737b6.poster.avif?t=1774366409\" width=608 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/a2ba75f22cdc504d55f29cfe779737b6.webm?t=1774366409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/a2ba75f22cdc504d55f29cfe779737b6.mp4?t=1774366409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/2399a9e6c5627ec934cf8fd52bb493dc.avif?t=1774366409\" width=600 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-style <strong>FANTASY BEAT'EM'UP / HACK'N'SLASH</strong>, inspired by classic cult games of 90s! Gore, weapons, armor, skills - what's not to love? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gold edition of the original game - MannaRites - which was warmly received by players:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>90% on Steam, 4.7 on Google Play</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/4eae29bfe91a8a2a888b66b771955c9d.avif?t=1774366409\" width=1248 height=259 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why Gold Edition though? Why pay for the free game?<br>Well, Gold edition is created to rethink and refine some of the gameplay features and balance of the original game and to add some asked features! And also - well, let's be honest here - to raise some financial support for the Chapter 2 development! So if you're waiting for C2 - please consider supporting us by getting the Gold edition!  <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/720dcc04b52230c3833f51ebf091ceb9.avif?t=1774366409\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone or with a friend and, as mighty <strong>WARRIOR</strong>, agile <strong>ACROBAT </strong>or powerful <strong>MAGUS</strong>, master the art of fighting. Game features three levels of difficulty - for new players, veterans and seasoned hardcore players. Fully original soundtrack and voiced dialogues will help you to immerse yourself into the mysterious world of Ijmeria and defend your people against brutal invaders! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/3f3269471034383d5234824325a91007.avif?t=1774366409\" width=800 height=288 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/41c98b3cf394a4555149dc13f4bdadbe.avif?t=1774366409\" width=600 height=70 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >unique <strong>FANTASY</strong> setting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>skill-based</strong> combat with <strong>special moves, throws, blocks and ripostes</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >army of enemies with <strong>unique behavior</strong> and combat moves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >hours long story-driven adventure, featuring <strong>NPCs and quests</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >fully voiced dialogues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >open map to explore and choose your path</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>loot system</strong> - weapons, armor, potions and items to find, equip and use</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RPG system</strong> - combat moves, skills and perks to master</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >original soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/a2ba75f22cdc504d55f29cfe779737b6.poster.avif?t=1774366409\" width=608 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/a2ba75f22cdc504d55f29cfe779737b6.webm?t=1774366409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/a2ba75f22cdc504d55f29cfe779737b6.mp4?t=1774366409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/2399a9e6c5627ec934cf8fd52bb493dc.avif?t=1774366409\" width=600 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-style <strong>FANTASY BEAT'EM'UP / HACK'N'SLASH</strong>, inspired by classic cult games of 90s! Gore, weapons, armor, skills - what's not to love? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gold edition of the original game - MannaRites - which was warmly received by players:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>90% on Steam, 4.7 on Google Play</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2509720/extras/4eae29bfe91a8a2a888b66b771955c9d.avif?t=1774366409\" width=1248 height=259 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why Gold Edition though? Why pay for the free game?<br>Well, Gold edition is created to rethink and refine some of the gameplay features and balance of the original game and to add some asked features! And also - well, let's be honest here - to raise some financial support for the Chapter 2 development! So if you're waiting for C2 - please consider supporting us by getting the Gold edition!  <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\